Home sits on just over half acre of level land with creek at back of the property, large yard for a garden, children or pets. being sold ''as is'' As with all Real Estate transactions Buyer(s) should verify all information independently including HOA info and Square Footage. Equal housing opportunity. Most information from Tax records and not verified by listing agent/Company.
